<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n東周列國&middot;春秋篇<br />\n大秦帝國系列<br />\n漢武大帝<br />\n94三國演義<br />\n貞觀之治<br />\n大宋提刑官<br />\n大明王朝1566<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雍正王朝<br />\n走向共和<br />\n我的團長我的團<br />\n人間正道是滄桑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n點估到而家歷史劇變左瀕危劇種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0e789f9c3b909d65fba5cd8d94ea3de20d0473","tid":832071,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"879e19bbe2e0584953c723efd3e10f6dcbe75977","tid":832071,"uid":121697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e6d7a9bdece3026bf096a0cfb8a9ff87c62d18f","tid":832071,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fe6a68365594be950ab4088b1e7aede588a707e","tid":832071,"uid":119290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-23T02:22:27.000Z","msg":"光武中興"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:17:08.000Z","msg":"光武太屈機,佢自己一個已經勁過晒D手下,人品好又愛老婆,成個完人咁,會拍得好尷尬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而劉邦呢D市井廢柴逆襲打贏貴族後代啱小市民睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:27:39.000Z","msg":"劉秀可以拍套超能力特技電影<br />\n黎個大隕石術收尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n按正常拍一定離撚曬地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-24T06:36:22.000Z","msg":"果段似吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,可以skip咗佢既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實都唔至於無野好寫,個傳奇性在於原本佢呀哥野心大過佢好多,但兩兄弟後來比更始帝逼害,呀哥仲死埋,自己韜光養晦等機會發圍最後成功咁囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,D大小戰役佢實在太順風順水無咩好寫,要重點講下點爭取地方豪強支持+同佢地博奕"},{"pid":"ab3527b06fb41a20fa1e18ecfda1ec5fa0258a66","tid":832071,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf87b7114a74ba